# Voce UI Design System

## Design reference: Notion
- White or very light grey backgrounds (#FAFAFA for page bg, white for cards)
- Borders: 1px solid hsl(var(--border)) — subtle, never heavy
- Generous whitespace — padding-4 minimum on cards, padding-6 on page sections
- Typography hierarchy through weight: font-semibold for titles, font-normal for body
- Muted text: text-muted-foreground for secondary content
- No gradients, no heavy shadows (shadow-sm maximum on cards)
- Hover states: bg-accent (light grey fill) only — never colour changes on hover

## Component library: shadcn/ui
Always use shadcn/ui primitives. Never write raw HTML form elements.
Import from @/components/ui/[component].
Before writing a custom component, check if a shadcn equivalent exists.

## Buttons
- Primary actions: <Button> (default variant)
- Secondary / outline actions: <Button variant="outline">
- Destructive: <Button variant="destructive">
- Ghost / nav items: <Button variant="ghost">
- Never use raw <button> tags in UI components

## Cards
Consistent card pattern for all content cards:
<div className="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4 shadow-sm">

## Badges and status pills
Use <Badge> from shadcn for all status indicators.
- Active / success: green override className="bg-green-100 text-green-800 border-green-200"
- Warning / paused: amber className="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 border-amber-200"
- Neutral / muted: <Badge variant="secondary">

## Loading states
Always show a loading state on every async action.
Disable the triggering button during loading.
Use <Loader2 className="h-4 w-4 animate-spin" /> from lucide-react.
Never leave a button in a state where double-submit is possible.

## Toasts
Use the existing toast system in this codebase — do not introduce a new one.
- Success: default/green variant
- Error: destructive variant
- Always fire a toast on async action completion (success or failure)

## Forms
- Labels always above inputs
- Placeholder text shows examples, never instructions ("e.g. AI agents" not "Enter your topic")
- Required fields marked with *
- Error messages shown below the field in text-destructive text-sm
- Never use raw <input> or <textarea> — use shadcn Input and Textarea

## Empty states
Every list or data view must have an empty state.
Pattern: centred container, muted icon (h-12 w-12), font-semibold title,
text-muted-foreground description, optional CTA Button.
Never show a blank white page.

## Mobile
- Sidebar collapses to bottom tab bar on < 768px
- Grid layouts: 3col desktop → 2col tablet → 1col mobile
- Touch targets minimum h-9 (36px) for all interactive elements
- Test truncation on long strings — use truncate or line-clamp-N

## Sidebar nav items
Pattern for all sidebar nav items:
<Button
  variant="ghost"
  className={cn(
    "w-full justify-start gap-2 h-9 px-3 font-normal",
    isActive && "bg-accent text-accent-foreground font-medium"
  )}
>
  <Icon className="h-4 w-4" />
  Label
</Button>
Active state: check usePathname() — active if pathname === href or pathname.startsWith(href).

## Icons
Use lucide-react exclusively. Never use emoji as icons in UI components.
Consistent sizes: h-4 w-4 for inline/nav icons, h-5 w-5 for card icons,
h-8 w-8 or h-12 w-12 for empty state illustrations.

## Page headers
Consistent page header pattern:
<div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
  <div>
    <h1 className="text-2xl font-semibold">Page Title</h1>
    <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Subtitle</p>
  </div>
  <div>{/* action buttons */}</div>
</div>

## Cron handlers — never touch
Never modify files in src/app/api/cron/. These are protected.

## Auth pattern
Use the existing requireAuth() or middleware pattern. Never hardcode userId.
Tag any userId usage with // STAGE2: replace with auth.uid() if it uses 'owner'.

## Exact token values (use these, not approximations)
- Page background: #F7F7F7
- Card background: #FFFFFF
- Border: #E5E7EB
- Text primary: #111827
- Text secondary: #6B7280
- Text muted: #9CA3AF
- Brand: #2563EB
- Brand light bg: #EFF6FF
- Shadow card: 0 1px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.07), 0 1px 2px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.07)
- Nav item height: py-1.5 (not h-9)
- Nav icon size: h-[15px] w-[15px]
- Nav text size: text-[13.5px]
- Page title: text-[22px] font-semibold
- Card title: text-[15px] font-semibold
- Body text: text-[13.5px]
- Small/meta text: text-[12px] or text-[11px]
